high_descs: turn around and move to the table
pick up the knife from the table that is to the right of the rectangular object
turn to the right and move to the sink
put the knife in to the sink, turn on the water to rinse off the knife, turn off the water and remove the knife from the sink
turn around and move to the table on the right and turn to face the left side of the table
put the knife on to the table between the spoon and the other silver butter knife
anns.task_desc: put a clean knife on to the table

high_descs: Turn around and walk up to the brown kitchen table.
Pick up the knife that is to the left of the tomato on the table.
Turn to your right, walk up to the gray marble sink.
Rinse the knife off in the sink before taking it back out.
Turn around and walk back to the brown kitchen table.
Place the butter knife between the spoon and the other butter knife on the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean knife on the kitchen table.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the wooden table across the room.
Pick up the butter knife, between the cooking spoon, and the tomato, on the table.
Turn to your right and go to the sink.
Place the knife in the sink, turn the water on, rinse off the knife, turn the water off, and remove the knife from the sink.
Turn around and go back to the table on your right.
Place the knife back on the table, between the spoon and the other butter knife.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean knife on the table.
